[00:45.24]'Can you tell me the way to King Street, please?'|“请问您能告诉我去King Street的路吗？”
[00:51.12]The man smiled pleasantly.|那个男人愉快地笑了。
[00:54.68]He did not understand English!|他不懂英语！
